divs: Sighting DetailsI was at my vacations in the Pyramids, Cairo. I was on the camel heading away from the pyramids, when doing this, I was taking photos with my galaxy S3, with the frontal camera. Taking a lot of photos. But I did not realize the UFO until I got home, when I started to look at the photos. I Thought immediately that it is a UFO. Amazing indeed.
